extendedInfo.description: Socialize with other singers and access your own Singers video page. A brand new feel in Social Networking amongst individuals who share the same magical, in-depth passion talented artist naturally gain.Easily browse around and witness the talent potential members have. Share your videos, thoughts and love for music delivered through this new mobile App.The concept behind the development of this wonderful App was powered by the fact that singers need an out-let to express there inner-growing talents all under one platform that provides support through an environment of musical appreciation and understanding.To: People who like music and like to sing... Music and singing is a beautiful thing. If you got it, show it... and if you don't yet, practice. This NEW App is a must have in the App collection.
